## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of current data and the inherent biases in the sources used. The analysis primarily focuses on the negative aspects of social media, potentially overlooking the benefits and positive impacts. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of social media platforms means that new risks and challenges may emerge that are not covered in this report.

